_sText:
Hunger Games
==================
	This is a new mod called hunger games, where you have to fight for your life finding boxes to get weapons and kill your enemies.

Game Instructions
------------------
You start in a cage where you have 30 seconds to plan what you are going to do, you dont start with any weapons so you gotta find boxes to get weapons, every box has a random spawned weapon, except for those in the middle.
Scavenge around the map and watch out for enemies. The last person alive shall become the victor!

Whats new?
------------------
Optimizing was a big part of the final version, so thats what we did, the castle has been recreated, so people may have higher fps near the castle.

We also fixed some textures

New Project
==================
[HG_Stranded](http://gamebanana.com/projects/34709 "HG_Stranded")

> [Hunger Games Beta TRAILER](http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-JBKjFgS4cg&feature=youtu.be "Hunger Games Beta TRAILER")
This is my fist CSS map release.

Map Name: hellscrypt

Author Michael Russell a.k.a. Hellbinder
hellbinder@comcast.net

Game Type: Zombie, I wouldnt use this map for any other game type.

The zip file contains the following files:

hellscrypt.bsp
hellscrypt.nav
hellscrypt.res

The zip file also contains the two folders:

decals
sound

To install place hellscrypt.bsp and hellscrypt.nav into your map folder..example:

C:\Program Files\Steam\SteamApps\youraccountname\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps

*This example is from a Vista machine the folder might be differently placed on an XP machine*


Place the decals folder into the following directory:

C:\Program Files\Steam\SteamApps\youraccountname\counter-strike source\cstrike\materials


Place the sound folder into the following directory:

C:\Program Files\Steam\SteamApps\youraccountname\counter-strike source\cstrike

If you did everything ok the map should be ready to play. The file: hellscrypt.res is for
running the map on a server. If you want to use the map on your server put this file into your map directory
along with the other files as instructed above.

Thanks

Map Name: HeLLscraper
Version: 1.0

Description: Yes, I agree. The Counter-Terrorists have a huge advantage over the Terrorists. But If the Terrorists use their Flashbangs properly..
^^
They can easily pwn the Terrorists. Now it is advisable to Restrict the AWP sniper rifle. But Youre the admin.. Youre Choice.
Both Teams Spawn perpendicular to each other! Buy your guns ASAP to avoid getting shot from the oppositions Spawn!
Once Your Guns are bought jump into the Teleportation Fence and BEGIN TO FIGHT!
Extract the .RAR File to your cstrike folder within your steamapps. There is also a .NAV for BOTs!
Enjoy!
www.hellclan.co.uk

This is a map, that i know there is a mod for, and you could put the mod in with it, but i just want to say, that i made this map-TYPE. Not the mod, TYPE. = D

A few things. 

1. This is made by me, [F]ox.

2. If you want to make remakes of it, PLEASE ASK ME.

3. It has a custom texture in it...

___:::___!!!Things about the map!!!___:::___

It is headshots only. This is a beta release, so i will be working on it, although it is about 95% done. There is one problem, sometimes, you can get an occasional body shot (lol body shots), but that doesn't happen every kill. This map is basically for headshot practice only, and it actually is really fun. 

After 120 seconds (2 minutes), the walls will go down, take your weapons, and give you knives, and the final people will be left to knife at the end of the round. Another thing i need to fix, is if someone dies, and the doors go down, you can go back and get their weapons. I will work on this, and will have it in the next release.

If you put this in your server, please tell me, because i would love to play it somewhere.
Also please rate this. I know it's not the greatest, but i tried to be creative with a map and that's what i came up with.
I would recommend 5-10 players, although it fits 16 slots (maybe 17)
Also, i would restrict snipers.

I hope you enjoy this, and i hope you tell people around about the map and me. I am open to ideas, and would like to see some.

Enjoy!!!
